{
  "stem": "12462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [CLEARS THROAT] his property, or the property of his family, still remained, so that he was a fairly wealthy man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came from a rather distinguished family in-- property-wise, in Germany, anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had he lived there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The defendant, Schacht, had, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He'd lived in the United States for a time, but not Schirach.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Fritzsche had been a well-known journalist for the conservative newspapers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Goebbels, the Reich Propaganda Ministry-- head of the Reich Propaganda Ministry-- thought he was very able.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he called him in and said, I want you to become one of the leaders, with respect to the press of Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Fritzsche accepted and also then became a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was, I think, about April, only four months after Hitler came to-- to power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fritzsche was given the task of collecting materials from the various agencies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would pass this to Otto Dietrich, who was the Reich Press Chief.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He and Goebbels were kind of-- although, the press chief, Otto Goebbels, was underneath Goebbels in some way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I mispronounced-- I took the wrong word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Although Dietrich was underneath Goebbels to some extent, he also traveled with Hitler and had a very separate in-road to Hitler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Fritzsche was in a position of having to get instructions, you might say, from two top guys and get this converted to language which was satisfactory to both of them, which was quite an art.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he would present paroles to the press.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he did this regularly during the immediate years before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, before each invasion, the press would be colored, somewhat, in terms of what the objects were of the Nazis in invading a country and so forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
